column1: #Text=I think people are often quite surprised by wheelchair basketball , what it is when they actually see it .
#Text=I think the name " wheelchair " basketball means disability obviously , but when you watch it there 's nothing about disability to it at all .
#Text=Just that we use wheelchairs , and that 's it .
